revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yarnalls}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarnall'' is the 20780<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1271 individuals. ''Yarnall'' is most common among White (96.54%) individuals.
